author: Herald News Staff
title: Case at Bourne football to resume tonight at 7
text: Case at Bourne football to resume tonight at 7 The Case Cardinals will make another trip down the Cape tonight when they resume their South Coast Conference football game against the Bourne Canalmen. Comment The Herald News, Fall River, MA By Herald News Staff Posted Oct. 10, 2015 at 10:03 AM Updated at 10:10 AM Posted Oct. 10, 2015 at 10:03 AM Updated at 10:10 AM The Case Cardinals will make another trip down the Cape tonight when they resume their South Coast Conference football game against the Bourne Canalmen. Because of lightning Friday night, the game was halted with 6:57 left in the second quarter with Bourne leading 14-6. The game will be picked up where it left off at 7 p.m. tonight. No admission will be charged. By Herald News Staff The Herald News, Fall River, MA By Herald News Staff Posted Oct. 10, 2015 at 10:03 AM Updated at 10:10 AM
